reviewText: This movie was great! Love seeing the story of this comedy legend.  As a poor person struggling with mental health issues also, she gives me hope, to make something of myself someday.  Would like to see this on dvd.
Was only copy they had wish it was on DVD but works great on my VCR. Love it very funny. I wish they'd make an updated Biography about Roseanne.
I really enjoyed this movie, Denny Dillon gives the performance of a lifetime, please get this if you love Roseanne. It's REALLY good.
